milestones.description: Dickie Bird has broken the record for officiating the most ODIs (6) as an umpire, going past Constant
Rod Marsh has broken the record for most dismissals (14) in ODIs, going past Alan Knott's 13
Alvin Kallicharran has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (62) in an innings in ODIs for WI, going past Fredericks's 46
Dennis Lillee has become the top wicket-taker for AUS in ODIs with 11 wickets, going past Mallett's 10
Clive Lloyd has broken the record for most ODIs (3) as captain for WI, going past Rohan Kanhai
Fredericks has scored 2 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for WI breaking Rohan Kanhai's record
Greg Chappell has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (10) for AUS, going past Ian Chappell
Keith Boyce has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for WI, going past Fredericks
Rod Marsh and Ross Edwards's 99-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 26 between Rod Marsh and Greg Chappell
